job_history.work_description: Work with personal healthy lifestyle and training clients to determine overall health, nutrition, and fitness goals, then tailor workout and nutrition programs to help clients meet goals. Developed personal brand and do client outreach using social media and online tools such as Instagram, Facebook, Google+, etc.
Manage 16 Personal trainers. Oversee All Operations on the floor/group training. Conducted weekly Training Meetings. Schedule Client appointments. Front Desk customer service. Prepare weekly Reports.
